CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 11, 1950, pg. 12 reads: "Achievement Club Chapters - Two new chapters in Wilkinsburg became a part of the National Achievement Clubs, Inc., recently. Members representing Achievement Chapter 26 are seated, left to right: Mmes, Janet Roberts, Eva Malone, treasurer; Bernice Tarpley, and Dorothy Taliaferro, president.  Achievement Chapter 20 members are standing left to right: The Misses Louise Williams, Frances Clark, Marian Parker, Mildred Bivins, president; Emma Bivins, Jacqueline Dudley and Lunella Bradley. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Achievement Club 26 members, seated, left to right: Janet Roberts, Eva Malone, Bernice Tarpley, and Dorothy Taliaferro; Club 20 members, standing, left to right: Louise Williams, Frances Clark, Marian Parker, Mildred Bivins, Emma Bivins, Jacqueline Dudley, and Lunella Bradley, posed in brick walled interior
